reviewText: when these actors are interviewed alone, much different outcome. it was a bit odd and mostly uncomfortable to watch as a big fan of the show.
A must watch for fans of the show .Loved it!!.
very bad video quality. I would have expected better.

This is a great cast interview panel. It has really funny moments and the dynamic between Michael Sheen and Lizzy Caplan is great. It gives you insight into the relationships between the actors on the show as well as how the show came about. Highly recommend for Masters of Sex fans!
